{"tid":2377890,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登政府發聲挺台！美國務院促北京停止施壓台灣　將深化與台關係","createTime":"2021-01-24T04:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T04:57:55.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e93ab3862e97f62ad89aa8b0b18d9020354bc2","tid":2377890,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"中國昨（23）派13架共機闖我西南空域，為今年以來最高單日擾台架次紀錄。美國國務院<br />\n於美國時間23日敦促北京政府停止對台施壓，且將會深化美台關係。國務院發言人普萊斯<br />\n（Ned Price）23日透過聲明表示，「我們敦促北京停止對台灣的軍事、外交、經濟壓力<br />\n，與台灣民選代表進行有意義的對話。」<br />\n聲明指出，美國現已關切注意到，中國不斷試圖威脅鄰居的行為模式，這也包括台灣在內<br />\n，「我們將與夥伴、盟友站在一起，促進我們在印太地區的共同繁榮、安全及價值觀&mdash;範<br />\n圍也涵蓋深化我們與民主台灣關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210124/1905911.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20210124%2F1905911.htm&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TalgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=5f3a64fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210124/1905911.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5b3983e89950b54d1a9743cf0455565b4f22c37c","tid":2377890,"uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:11:36.000Z","msg":"口交"},{"pid":"020f6e0bc3715b155db482bc294257baf4a25d7c","tid":2377890,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:12:01.000Z","msg":"支那韭菜崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf05f1c1b930c5f8342d3c9f8128689ecbd2cd2","tid":2377890,"uid":167394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b3983e89950b54d1a9743cf0455565b4f22c37c","tid":2377890,"uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:11:36.000Z","msg":"口交"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:16:26.000Z","msg":"中國外交部：不得干預內政"},{"pid":"fab966b63d838783c1d54c37358d8a7ea95d8263","tid":2377890,"uid":299694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"r